      "content": "thanks. it's not iterating the whole mapping, it's just a single key update. i think it's related to how the state is being modified. here's the snippet:\n\nfunction updateBalance(address _user, uint256 _amount) public {\n    balances[_user] += _amount;\n    totalLiquidity += _amount;\n}\n\nit's a very standard update, so i don't get why it's hitting the gas limit on larger scales. any ideas?",
